                            </label>
                            <ul className="list-disc pl-10 mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                                <li>T├ái khoß║ún sß║╜ sß╗¡ dß╗Ñng Email ß╗ƒ tr├¬n ─æß╗â ─æ─âng nhß║¡p</li>
                                <li>Mß║¡t khß║⌐u ngß║½u nhi├¬n sß║╜ ─æ╞░ß╗úc gß╗¡i vß╗ü Email</li>
