                    <p className="font-medium">Mß║╣o: ─Éß╗â ─æß║ít ─æß╗Ö ch├¡nh x├íc tß╗æt nhß║Ñt</p>
                    <ul className="mt-1 space-y-0.5 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">
