                    </button>
                </div>

                {/* Content */}
                <div className="p-6">
                    <p className="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">
                        Chß╗ìn lß╗¢p mß╗¢i ─æß╗â chuyß╗ân hß╗ìc sinh. Lß╗ïch sß╗¡ ─æ─âng k├╜ c┼⌐ sß║╜ ─æ╞░ß╗úc bß║úo l╞░u.
                    </p>
                    <div className="space-y-4">
                        <div>
                            <label className="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1.5">Lß╗¢p mß╗¢i <span className="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                            <div className="relative">
                                <select
                                    value={selectedClassId}
                                    onChange={(e) => setSelectedClassId(e.target.value)}
                                    className="w-full pl-4 pr-10 py-2.5 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 text-gray-900 text-sm rounded-lg focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 block p-2.5 outline-none transition-all"
                                >
                                    <option value="">-- Chß╗ìn lß╗¢p mß╗¢i --</option>
