                                <div className="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
                                    <Info className="w-4 h-4 text-amber-600" />
                                    <p className="text-sm font-bold text-amber-800">L╞░u ├╜ nhß║¡p ─æiß╗âm</p>
                                </div>
                                <ul className="text-[11px] text-amber-800/70 space-y-2 ml-4 list-disc font-medium leading-relaxed">
                                    <li>Chß╗ë nhß║¡p ─æiß╗âm cho hß╗ìc sinh trong danh s├ích mß║╖c ─æß╗ïnh.</li>
                                    <li>─Éiß╗âm sß╗æ hß╗úp lß╗ç trong khoß║úng tß╗½ <span className="font-bold text-amber-900">0 ─æß║┐n 10</span>.</li>
                                    <li>Sß╗¡ dß╗Ñng dß║Ñu chß║Ñm <span className="font-bold text-amber-900">(.)</span> cho phß║ºn thß║¡p ph├ón.</li>
                                    <li><span className="font-bold text-rose-600">Tuyß╗çt ─æß╗æi kh├┤ng</span> thay ─æß╗òi cß║Ñu tr├║c c├íc cß╗Öt/d├▓ng mß║½u.</li>
